title: The twelve Irish Tenors in Concert 2008 ENG-ITA (musicfromrizzo)
description:
This group of Irish Tenors bring us some Irish music long with several
Italian selections too (including a Sinatra favourite - That's Life)

One of their members is from Norway by the way - and he says
he grew up listening to Italian music - good for him!

(Downloaded from the net years ago - don't remember the source - sorry)

(embedded jpg for you in each mp3 to improve the download we obtained, along with the particular comment regarding the music tastes of at least one of the
Irish singers that we wanted to make as noted above)

Song listings from CD: (192k mp3)

Cockles and Mussels (Molly Malone)
Rhythm of Life
The Rose
Irish Medley: The Wild Rover / Rosie O'Grady / MacNamara's Band
La Donna E Mobile
Funiculi, Funicula
Nessun Dorma (Pavarotti favourite)
You Raise Me Up
Danny Boy
That's Life (Sinatra Hit)
Do You Hear the People Sing?
Bring Him Home
You'll Never Walk Alone (Elvis number)


enjoy and please do seed if you care to

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
